<div>
  <h2> Quips API </h2>
  <ol>
    <li><%=link_to 'Create', :controller => 'api_keys', :action => 'new' %> an API key </li>
    <li>Send a POST request with the following keys and information:
      <ul>
        <li>Post to: http://stillraging.net/resquip/quips</li>
        <li>apikey = (your API key)</li>
        <li>quip[date] = MM-DD-YY (optional)</li>
        <li>quip[quip] = (quip string here)</li>
      </ul>
    <li>...</li>
    <li>Profit!</li>
  </ol>
  You can test the string using curl, like so: 
  <pre>
  curl -d "apikey=7e9e653fa6c1a83050b618a72&amp;quip[date]=2010-05-12&amp;quip[quip]=testing;" stillraging.net/resquip/quips
  </pre>
</div>
    
